data.description: ARE YOU LOOKING FOR A HOME/MINI FARM WITH PLENTY OF PRIVACY WITHOUT AN HOA? THIS 3 BEDROOM 2 BATH HOME SITTING ON OVER 4 ACRES OF LAND OFFERS A SENSE OF PRIVACY AND TRANQUILITY. THE HOME FEATURES AN OPEN FLOOR PLAN WITH A WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE, A STEP DOWN KITCHEN WITH PLENTY OF CABINET SPACE AS WELL AS AN ISLAND IN THE KITCHEN. THE MASTER BEDROOM FEATURES A WALK IN CLOSET, DUAL SINKS, A WALK IN SHOWER AS WELL A GARDEN TUB! THE HOME IS LOCATED JUST MINUTES FROM THE OVER 53 THOUSAND ACRE GOETHE STATE FOREST AS WELL AS LAKE ROUSSEAU! PLENTY OF ROOM FOR THE PETS TO ROAM OUTSIDE AS WELL AS STORAGE SPACE FOR THE TOYS AS THERE IS 2 STORAGE SHEDS ON THE PROPERTY. THERE IS AN ADDITIONAL WELL AND SEPTIC ON THE PROPERTY BUT THE CONDITION IS UNKNOWN. THE HOME NEEDS A LITTLE TLC BUT IS PRICED ACCORDINGLY.
